            <p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 9pt; position: fixed; bottom: 0; width:100%; text-align: center"><b>EAN Registration Management</b><br/>
                Breite Gasse 4/7, 1070 Vienna, Austria<br/>
                registration@ean.org, 00431889050325</p>
